{"tid":1431240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警自食其果害家人","createTime":"2019-08-08T02:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T03:19:28.000Z","uid":281444,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d7c613c97b597c60f97d978932e22914bbe9e403","tid":1431240,"uid":281444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"當你班黑警，唔跟遊戲規則玩時，<br />\n市民做咩仲要跟遊戲規則?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地有使用大殺傷力武器權力，<br />\n我地普通市民只係有血肉之軀，<br />\n<br />\n你話我地蒙曬面搞事，<br />\n所以唔須要帶委任証，<br />\n因我地會被政府<span style=\"color: red;\">濫告重判</span>，<br />\n但你地可以合法<span style=\"color: red;\">殺人無罪</span>，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">依家成手血先怕被起底?</span></span><br />\n做黑警、依家就係<span style=\"color: red;\">一件醜事</span>，<br />\n呢個<span style=\"color: red;\">社會觀念亦會延續比後代知道</span>，<br />\n變成<span style=\"color: red;\">家規</span>、香港社會一個<span style=\"color: red;\">禁忌</span>，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實係你自己傷害緊家人</span>，<br />\n係你既職業令家人蒙羞，<br />\n你往後既後代繼續蒙羞，<br />\n<br />\n當個孫知道啊爺做黑警 會點睇?<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"74b9d7806fb06b34a52ea65c65bbb526444f5451","tid":1431240,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T02:59:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mb1WCuf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMb1WCuf.png&h=b7fb75b0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSSyEHB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSSyEHB.png&h=845f98c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/105854_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F08%2F105854_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=4d42c653&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/08/105855_0f6641dea71077